dc_title_s: Chinae, olim sinarum regionis, nova descriptio; auctore Ludovico Georgio.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Oriented with north to the right. Includes ill. and decorative cartouches. On verso: La China, p. 118. From Ortellius' Theatrum orbis terrarum. 1 map: hand col.; 35 x 45 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Barbuda, Luis Jorge de, fl. 1575-1599.,Ortelius, Abraham, 1527-1598.
